OL,3,C'Serious fire' rips through restaurant
OL,4,Cin Guernsey
OL,6,FA "serious fire" has ripped through a
OL,7,Frestaurant in Guernsey producing a
OL,8,F"toxic smoke flume".
OL,10,FIslanders have been warned to keep
OL,11,Ftheir doors and windows closed if they
OL,12,Fsee smoke coming towards them,
OL,13,Ffollowing a fire at Octopus Restaurant
OL,14,Fin .
OL,16,FHowever, Guernsey Fire Service
OL,17,FIncident Commander, Danny Joyce has
OL,18,Fstressed: "It is not a public safety
OL,19,Fhazard."
