OL,6,FEmergency services attended the blaze
OL,7,Fat 4.09am on Saturday 24 February.
OL,9,FCommander Joyce said: "Everybody is
OL,10,Ffine there were no people in the
OL,11,Fbuilding at the time."
OL,13,FHe also confirmed "there is no gas in
OL,14,Fthe building" as gas bottles were
OL,15,Fremoved from the site.
OL,17,FHe added: "Unfortunately, the fire was
OL,18,Fin the roof void and began to spread.
