OL,6,F"It became apparent that it was too
OL,7,Fdangerous to fight the fire from
OL,8,Fwithin the building. So we withdrew
OL,9,Ffrom outside the building and since
OL,10,Fthen we've been fighting the fire from
OL,11,Foutside."
OL,13,FGuernsey Civil Protection is diverting
OL,14,Ftraffic as roads surrounding La
OL,15,FVallette are closed.
OL,17,FBoth South Esplanade and Val Des
OL,18,FTerres are also closed.
