OL,6,FGuernsey Police Duty Inspector, Adam
OL,7,FMiller thanked volunteers for
OL,8,Fassisting with necessary road closures
OL,9,Fand asked the public to work with them
OL,10,Fso that emergency services could
OL,11,Fcontinue to access the site.
OL,13,FHe added that all lines of inquiry are
OL,14,Fopen and has appealed for witnesses.
